WEBVTT

01:49:58.399 --> 01:49:59.399
As for his "planning"...

01:50:00.024 --> 01:50:02.108
He was able to move
my son's remains from there

01:50:02.108 --> 01:50:04.983
only because he had
many years on his side.

01:50:05.608 --> 01:50:06.691
Luck!

01:50:06.691 --> 01:50:09.649
It's sheer luck that he got away
with it for this long!
